    <title>用成本最低的方式解决hexo博客部署在Gihub_Pages在国内访问慢的问题</title>
    <link href="/2024/08/17/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%9C%A8Gihub-Pages%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%85%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <url>/2024/08/17/%E7%94%A8%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%9C%A8Gihub-Pages%E5%9C%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E6%85%A2%E7%9A%84%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>相信不少小伙伴都在使用 GitHub Pages 提供的免费静态网站托管来搭建自己的博客，但是因为特殊原因，使用 GitHub Pages 搭建的博客在国内访问速度极慢，因此很多小伙伴只能转战国内付费的服务器和 CDN。</p><p>然而，国内的CDN都需要域名先备案，不然无法使用。使用CloudFlare的CDN服务在国内的访问速度也并不理想。终于，我找到了相对完美的解决方案，话不多说先上图：</p><p><img src="https://picgo.ningh.net/images_hgxk/image.9dcvwsxpa9.webp" alt="博客访问测速"></p><p>博客地址：<a href="http://blog.ningh.net/">http://blog.ningh.net</a> 欢迎各位小伙伴测速</p><p>原理很简单，笔者使用了一台香港的云服务器，实现了简单的流量转发和缓存。并且使用免费的picx图床解决了Fluid主题用Typora插入图片时无法渲染的问题。实测访问速度极快。对原理不清楚的小伙伴请百度搜索 ”正向代理“。</p><p>肯定有小伙伴要说，你都有香港云服务器了，你直接把博客部署到服务器上不就得?在这脱裤子放屁干嘛？原因很简单，之前购买云服务器的时候并没有想搭建博客，所以购买的配置非常低。我购买的是阿里云的香港云服务器，公网IP，1核CPU + 0.5G（实际上只有459MB）内存 + 20G硬盘的配置，每月200G的公网流量，五年只需270元，平均才4.2一个月。我觉得这样的配置无法支撑我的博客稳定运行五年，更何况在上面我还搭建了其他服务。</p><p>不知道活动还有没有过期，这里附上服务器购买教程：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/tolvip/p/18269541">https://www.cnblogs.com/tolvip/p/18269541</a></p><p>我们只需要准备一台海外云服务器（最好是香港，速度最快）和一个域名，接下来话不多说直接开始。</p><h1 id="解决Fluid主题用Typora插入图片时无法渲染的问题"><a href="#解决Fluid主题用Typora插入图片时无法渲染的问题" class="headerlink" title="解决Fluid主题用Typora插入图片时无法渲染的问题"></a>解决Fluid主题用Typora插入图片时无法渲染的问题</h1><p>这一步不是必须的，不介意的小伙伴可以直接跳过这一步。</p><p>最佳的解决方案是图床。我使用picx搭建图床，图片全部保存在Github仓库，然后使用jsDelivr CDN加速访问。picx搭建图床非常简单，傻瓜式操作，具体请参考<a href="https://picx-docs.xpoet.cn/usage-guide/get-start.html">PicX使用手册</a>。</p><p>使用jsDelivr加速也非常简单，只需要在图床设置中将图片链接规则切换为jsDelivr即可。</p><p><img src="https://picgo.ningh.net/images_hgxk/image.8z6g6171o6.webp" alt="将图片链接规则切换为jsDelivr"></p><p>这样操作完，其实在大陆已经可以成功访问图片了，但是速度还是不够快。</p><p><img src="https://picgo.ningh.net/images_hgxk/image.2h88cq3h80.webp" alt="cdn.jsdelivr.net测速"></p><p>cdn.jsdelivr.net在大陆节点很少，ping cdn.jsdelivr.net在大陆平均延迟450ms，实际下载一张图片可能延迟是2倍不止，这对读者是无法接受的。</p><p>正好cdn.jsdelivr.net在香港有节点，我用我的服务器ping延迟2ms，嘿嘿！</p><p><img src="https://picgo.ningh.net/images_hgxk/image.1hs4zk7fm0.webp"></p><p>所以我们可以用服务器代理一下，当用户请求一张图片时，先把请求发给我的服务器，然后我的服务器再去请求cdn.jsdelivr.net，实测大陆下载一张图片只需0.1s以内，快了十倍！</p><p>我们先配置PicX链接，流量中转的代码我后面会给出，小伙伴们只需复制粘贴修改即可。在图床设置-图片链接规则配置 中新建一条规则，添加并且将图片链接规则切换为你刚刚添加的规则即可。</p><p><img src="https://picgo.ningh.net/images_hgxk/image.41xzc7hv0w.webp" alt="添加规则"></p><p>接下来就是配置代理服务器了。在进行下一步之前，你需要：</p><ol><li><p>将域名解析到你的服务器</p><p>举例：</p><p>我使用blog.ningh.net中转博客流量，使用picx.ningh.net中转图床流量，这两个域名都解析到我的服务器。如果你不需要图床，那么配置一条记录即可。</p></li><li><p>服务器安装Python3环境</p></li><li><p>如果Github Pages 自定义了域名记得取消</p></li></ol><p>这三步不会的请自行百度，教程很多。</p><h1 id="使用Python实现一个简单的代理服务器"><a href="#使用Python实现一个简单的代理服务器" class="headerlink" title="使用Python实现一个简单的代理服务器"></a>使用Python实现一个简单的代理服务器</h1><p>先安装cachetools</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pip install cachetools<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当用户使用域名<code>blog.ningh.net</code>访问时，将请求正向代理到<code>https://kuhbz.github.io</code>；当用户使用<code>picx.ningh.net</code>访问时，将请求正向代理到<code>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net</code>，每接收一次请求都需要输出必要的日志。并且设置了缓存，加快了访问速度。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> http.server<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> urllib.request<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> logging<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> concurrent.futures<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> cachetools <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> TTLCache<br><br>PORT = <span class="hljs-number">80</span>  <br>CACHE_TTL = <span class="hljs-number">300</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 缓存的生存时间（秒）</span><br>CACHE_MAXSIZE = <span class="hljs-number">100</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># 缓存的最大条目数量</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建一个具有TTL的缓存</span><br>cache = TTLCache(maxsize=CACHE_MAXSIZE, ttl=CACHE_TTL)<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">ProxyHandler</span>(http.server.BaseHTTPRequestHandler):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">do_GET</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self</span>):<br>        host = <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.headers[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Host&#x27;</span>]<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 只需适当更改下面注释的部分即可</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># if host == &#x27;blog.ningh.net&#x27;:</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#     target_url = f&#x27;https://kuhbz.github.io&#123;self.path&#125;&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># elif host == &#x27;picx.ningh.net&#x27;:</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#     target_url = f&#x27;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net&#123;self.path&#125;&#x27;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.send_error(<span class="hljs-number">404</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;域名未找到&quot;</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span><br><br>        logging.info(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;代理请求 <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;host&#125;</span> 到 <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;target_url&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> target_url <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> cache:<br>            logging.info(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;从缓存中获取: <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;target_url&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.send_response(<span class="hljs-number">200</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.send_header(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Content-type&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;text/html&#x27;</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.end_headers()<br>            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.wfile.write(cache[target_url])<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.fetch_and_cache(target_url)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">fetch_and_cache</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, target_url</span>):<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> urllib.request.urlopen(target_url) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> response:<br>                content = response.read()<br>                cache[target_url] = content<br>                <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.send_response(response.status)<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> header <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> response.getheaders():<br>                    <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.send_header(header[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>], header[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>])<br>                <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.end_headers()<br>                <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.wfile.write(content)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> e:<br>            logging.error(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;代理请求出错: <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;e&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-variable language_">self</span>.send_error(<span class="hljs-number">500</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;内部服务器错误&quot;</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">run</span>(<span class="hljs-params">server_class=http.server.HTTPServer, handler_class=ProxyHandler</span>):<br>    logging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)<br>    server_address = (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>, PORT)<br>    httpd = server_class(server_address, handler_class)<br>    logging.info(<span class="hljs-string">f&quot;在端口 <span class="hljs-subst">&#123;PORT&#125;</span> 启动服务器&quot;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> concurrent.futures.ThreadPoolExecutor() <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> executor:<br>        executor.submit(httpd.serve_forever)<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="hljs-string">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:<br>    run()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>新建一个server.py文件，将修改后的代码粘贴进去，将文件上传至服务器root用户的家目录下，然后用root账号执行以下命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> ~<br>python server.py<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>看到这样的输出就是成功啦：</p><p><img src="https://picgo.ningh.net/images_hgxk/image.1seysr1jwq.webp" alt="启动服务"></p><p>实测资源占用率极低：</p><p><img src="https://picgo.ningh.net/images_hgxk/image.77dhb61io7.webp"></p><p>不会搭建的小伙伴也欢迎从<a href="http://blog.ningh.net/about/">我的博客</a>加我微信进群交流哈！</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
